import React from 'react'
import { Button, Container, Header, Segment } from 'semantic-ui-react'

export default function HomePage() {
    return (
        <Segment color='red' inverted style={{borderRadius:"0px", marginTop:"0px", height:"100vh"}}>
            <Header >
                WELCOME TO THE THORGE
            </Header>
            <Header as="h3">
                (A character forge made by Thor Hlavaty)
            </Header>
            <Button inverted>
                Forge a Character
            </Button>
            <Button inverted>
                Show me that which is Forged
            </Button>
        </Segment>
    )
}
